{"tid":1335953,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"說好的普選人大呢?　(香港需要三普選)","createTime":"2019-07-20T17:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T12:21:44.000Z","uid":99566,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c1388ebec1f83149fe7afb3ea86c0cff21dcbedc","tid":1335953,"uid":99566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:25:35.000Z","msg":"大家成日提雙普選，我記得早幾年有巴絲都提過香港仲有另一種選舉，就係港區人大選舉。<br />\n呢個時候又話要同內地宣傳，爭取D野，和理非係咪應該除左港區人大普選之外，都宣傳俾同胞內地人大都要落實普選呢？<br />\n<br />\n事實港區人大都係選舉產生，應該讓港人進一步融入國家，實現普選！<br />\n<br />\n記住：拆屋效應！！！五大訴求既雙普選要變三普選！！！"},{"pid":"31fb2ac88cbed3e8b2994780c224a30bb3cb6b5f","tid":1335953,"uid":512,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:26:21.000Z","msg":"大陸人既野唔關我事"},{"pid":"620131f35e5bd63c65b789293f06d2d48259ec8a","tid":1335953,"uid":107686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:26:25.000Z","msg":"good idea"},{"pid":"6895802f8e0be11229f4a29f67432812926d5ad1","tid":1335953,"uid":99566,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"31fb2ac88cbed3e8b2994780c224a30bb3cb6b5f","tid":1335953,"uid":512,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:26:21.000Z","msg":"大陸人既野唔關我事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:28:26.000Z","msg":"都話拆屋效應LO，呢個就係個屋頂呀屌"},{"pid":"e0fde1aac67f7e309248f8fd7d05b4e3769a34b2","tid":1335953,"uid":99566,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:33:44.000Z","msg":"港區人大係一國兩制下，香港人選舉產生出來既立法機關代表<br />\n佢地都無讀中國式大陸法法律，咪又係投票立中國既法<br />\n而且要破港獨既個標籤，又要做到拆屋效應，普選人大係一個好好既口號<br />\n香港幫內地同胞都維權架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1668a09853cd04d8ac367d80f2ae51e38b7740b","tid":1335953,"uid":189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:34:58.000Z","msg":"咁不如講埋普選國家主席"},{"pid":"12d74e0e0459ca287542be8f642833848a42975c","tid":1335953,"uid":99566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d1668a09853cd04d8ac367d80f2ae51e38b7740b","tid":1335953,"uid":189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:34:58.000Z","msg":"咁不如講埋普選國家主席"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:38:49.000Z","msg":"呢個人大真係香港人選出來既，只係一直冷處理少人提。呢個時候係咪用佢來搞拆屋理論，加快要政府執行訴求，就係符合目標既概念"},{"pid":"4949409e92c82169f498ce1433d361858db1d83b","tid":1335953,"uid":99566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:46:51.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"d846b83555ff276432582483de0d4f5c91a842f6","tid":1335953,"uid":99566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:05:12.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"2330d34bfca1b977acd96082cfdf91e147f958b1","tid":1335953,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T19:08:18.000Z","msg":"要求普選人大都好，等大陸少數心水清嘅人支持個成個運動<br />\n<br />\n大陸人一出聲就話要佢哋普選人大，突顯制度不公<br />\n<br />\n低成本火燒佢哋後爛"},{"pid":"9115b0d679fcd2cdaff9440eed1007ab1f610189","tid":1335953,"uid":99566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2330d34bfca1b977acd96082cfdf91e147f958b1","tid":1335953,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T19:08:18.000Z","msg":"要求普選人大都好，等大陸少數心水清嘅人支持個成個運動<br />\n<br />\n大陸人一出聲就話要佢哋普選人大，突顯制度不公<br />\n<br />\n低成本火燒佢哋後爛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T02:26:34.000Z","msg":"就係要燒大場火"},{"pid":"a47badf500e57b3dfa0481543969d7fb9c2ccdf4","tid":1335953,"uid":99566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:45:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9322850ba42d72375a781e668a1048a569025a86","tid":1335953,"uid":99566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:21:44.000Z","msg":"推~~~"}]}